<h2>Writing the Holocaust Today (Sammelband)</h2>
<h3>Critical Perspectives on Jonathan Littell’s The Kindly Ones</h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='1666'></abbr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
